# Atom Ocean Dark Syntax Theme

A subtle atom syntax theme based on Base16 Ocean Dark theme for Sublime Text.

**Credits** to [Chris Kempson - Base16 Ocean Dark](http://chriskempson.github.io/base16/#ocean)
